(2789, 1, '2018-01-19 00:02:28', '2018-01-19 00:02:28', '<p>[vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_inner-hero\" css=\".vc_custom_1516139500861{background-image: url(http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/inner-hero.jpg?id=2795) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h5>SERVICES</h5>\n<h1>Cannabis Analytical Testing</h1>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"lead-in\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2>What We Can Do</h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Hereâs a list of services that we provide for our clients.</span></p>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" el_id=\"service-accordion\"][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion c_icon=\"chevron\" active_section=\"\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Potency Testing\" tab_id=\"ac1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2>Using the most sophisticated microbiologic screening techniques available to science</h2>\n<p>Quality control measures and testing efforts are absolutely essential to be able to produce safe, consistent, and efficacious cannabis products to the public. Our staff contains nationally renowned experts in the field of cannabis testing who set the standard for accurate testing methods. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\".bg_callout\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3>We test for the following species:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>E. Coli</li>\n<li>Salmonella spp</li>\n<li>Aspergillus fumigatus</li>\n<li>Aspergillus flavus</li>\n<li>Aspergillus niger</li>\n<li>Aspergillus terreus</li>\n<li>Total Yeast and Mold</li>\n<li>Total Aerobic Plate Count</li>\n<li>Coliforms</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][