(2816, 1, '2018-01-18 22:36:37', '2018-01-18 22:36:37', '[vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"bg_inner-hero\" css=\".vc_custom_1516139500861{background-image: url(http://localhost:8888/belcosta/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/inner-hero.jpg?id=2795) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5>SERVICES</h5>\r\n<h1>Cannabis Analytical Testing</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"lead-in\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>What We Can Do</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Hereâs a list of services that we provide for our clients.</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" el_id=\"service-accordion\"][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion c_icon=\"chevron\" active_section=\"\"][vc_tta_section title=\"Potency Testing\" tab_id=\"ac1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Microbiological Testing\" tab_id=\"ac2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Using the most sophisticated microbiologic screening techniques available to science</h2>\r\nQuality control measures and testing efforts are absolutely essential to be able to produce safe, consistent, and efficacious cannabis products to the public. Our staff contains nationally renowned experts in the field of cannabis testing who set the standard for accurate testing methods. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_class=\".bg_callout\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>We test for the following species:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>E. Coli</li>\r\n 	<li>Salmonella spp</li>\r\n 	<li>Aspergillus fumigatus</li>\r\n 	<li>Aspergillus flavus</li>\r\n 	<li>Aspergillus niger</li>\r\n 	<li>Aspergillus terreus</li>\r\n 	<li>Total Yeast and Mold</li>\r\n 	<li>Total Aerobic Plate Count</li>\r\n 	<li>Coliforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"2813\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>How do we test for these microorganisms?</h2>\r\nâBelCosta Labs utilizes Medicinal Genomics PathogINDICAtor qPCR platform to extract and subsequently amplify pathogen DNA. This has major advantages over traditional plating due to increased sensitivity and specificity. In particular, this assay targets DNA sequences that are unique to each species of bacteria and fungi preventing any kind of potential false positives. â[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h6>01</h6>\r\n<h4>Shiga-toxin producing E. Coli (STEC)</h4>\r\nââSTECs are a type of disease causing bacteria that produces shiga toxin. The most common of these STECs is the O157:H7 serovar which can produce serious gastrointestinal illness.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h6>02</h6>\r\n<h4>âSalmonella spp.</h4>\r\nâââSalmonella is a group of gram-negative, rod shaped bacteria that cause typhoid fever, gastroenteritis, and other illnesses.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h6>03</h6>\r\n<h4>Aspergillus spp.</h4>\r\nâAspergillus is a t